The '''Re-Learning Circle''' was part of the [[Learning Circle]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Kegan/Legends|Kegan]]. It was an underground facility featuring solitary confinement cells and brainwashing sessions for enrolled youth. Students and infants at the Re-Learning Circle were usually sent there for consistent misbehavior or an incurable illness. [[V-Davi]] was among the students sent to the Re-Learning Circle for misbehavior. [[Olana Chion/Legends|O-Lana]] was sent there for her [[The Force/Legends|Force]] abilities, but she was eventually rescued by [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] and [[Siri Tachi/Legends|Siri Tachi]], who arranged to be sent there by misbehaving in the Learning Circle. Following this rescue, the population of Kegan found out about the Re-Learning Circle's similarities to a [[Prison/Legends|prison]] and voted to shut it down.

